snippet.title: Marksmen DLC Trailer - Arma III
snippet.description:
Hone your shooting skills and engage in ranged combat. The Arma III Marksmen DLC includes seven new weapons, two scopes, remote designators, ghillie suits, firing drills, and the Marksmen showcase scenario.

Follow Arma III at GameSpot.com!

Official Site - http://www.arma3.com/
